        "The projectile deals damage equal to half the Nightbane's Supernatural P.S. punch damage +1D6.",
        "Chance to knock targets flat (lose initiative and one attack): 25% against normal strength, 10% against Supernatural Strength or larger than 8 feet. Add +20% to these odds if the target is already off balance.",
